      "n": 40,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Zikreifi tee wiꞥnu apkai-\ntinaja Tukfneti/ un karrinaja\nwiꞥnu poſta Weetâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 41,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Jo tee kahrdinaja to\nSTIPRU DEEWU allach\nno jauna/ un likke tam Israeſta kuß eekſch Kama Dſihwoſteem.\nSwehtam Mehrkuß.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 42,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tee ne peeminneja wiꞥ-\nna Rohku/ nedß to Deenn/ kad\nwiꞥſch tohs no ta Prettineeka\nisglahbe.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 43,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad wiꞥſch fauwas Sih-\nmes parahdija Egiptes-Semmê/\nun jawus Brihnumus Joana\nLaufâ.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 44,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un pawehrtija wiꞥnu\nUppeß par Affinim/ un wiꞥnu\nStrautus/ ka tee dſert ue war-\nreja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 45,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch fuhtija ſtarp teem\nKukkaizus/ kas tohs ehde/ un\nWardes/ kas tohs jamaitaja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 46,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un dewe wiꞥnu Augtue-\nteem Spradscheem/ un wiꞥnu\nDarbu teem Giffneem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 47,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch nomaitaja wi-\nnu Wihna-Rohkus zaur Kruffu/\nun wiꞥnu Wihges-Rohkus ar\nleeleem Kruffs Asmiineem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 48,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch arrı nokawe wiꞥ-\nnu Lohpus ar Kruffu/ un wi-\nnu Sihkmagus ar Blahtmahm-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 49,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch fuhtija ſtarp teem\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 39,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "( ſtarp teem) faunus Engetug,\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 50,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch dfinnahs ar fa-\nwu Dutmibu probjam/un ne at-\nrahwe wiꞥzu Dwehteles no Nah-\nwes/ un nodeue wiꞥnu Lohpus\nMehram.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 51,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Wiꞥſch kawe wiſhus\nPirmdſimmufchus Egiptes-\nSemmiê/tohs pirmus Mantnee-\nkus eekſch Kama Dſihwoſteem.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 52,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wede faunus Landis\nka Awis/ un waddija tohs Tuk-\nnefi/ ka gannamu Pulku.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 53,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch waddija tohs\nbes Likſtahm/ ka tee ne bihjajahs/\nbet wiꞥnu Eenaidneekus aptlah-\nje ta Juhra.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 54,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un wiꞥſch wedde tohs fa-\nwäs fivehtâß Rohbeschâß / us\ntcho Kalnu/ fo wiꞥna labba Roh-\nka uſnehmuſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 55,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tas iſdsinne wiꞥnu\nPreekſchâ tohs Baganus/ un lik-\nke teem ar Auſli to eemantoja-\nnu Semmi iſmehroht/ un likke\ntahs Israëta Ziltis eekſch wiꞥnu\nMahjahm Dſihwoht-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 56,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Tattchu tee kahrdinaja\nun apkaitinaja to wiꞥnu-augstak\nDeewu / un ne turreja wiꞥna\nLeezibas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 57,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un tee atkahpe/ un pahr-\nlaſtija to Tizzibu/ itt ka wiꞥnu\nTehwi/ tee atmukke / ka weens\nflahbans Stohps.\n"
